{"tha-ap57:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap57:0.2":"Bijanivagga ","tha-ap57:0.3":"5 Opavayhattheraapadana ","tha-ap57:1.1":"“Padumuttarabuddhassa, ","tha-ap57:1.2":"ajaniyamadasaham; ","tha-ap57:1.3":"Niyyadetvana sambuddhe, ","tha-ap57:1.4":"agamasim sakam gharam. ","tha-ap57:2.1":"Devalo nama namena, ","tha-ap57:2.2":"satthuno aggasavako; ","tha-ap57:2.3":"Varadhammassa dayado, ","tha-ap57:2.4":"agacchi mama santikam. ","tha-ap57:3.1":"Sapattabharo bhagava, ","tha-ap57:3.2":"ajaneyyo na kappati; ","tha-ap57:3.3":"Tava sankappamannaya, ","tha-ap57:3.4":"adhivasesi cakkhuma. ","tha-ap57:4.1":"Agghapetva vatajavam, ","tha-ap57:4.2":"sindhavam sighavahanam; ","tha-ap57:4.3":"Padumuttarabuddhassa, ","tha-ap57:4.4":"khamaniyamadasaham. ","tha-ap57:5.1":"Yam yam yonupapajjami, ","tha-ap57:5.2":"devattam atha manusam; ","tha-ap57:5.3":"Khamaniyam vatajavam, ","tha-ap57:5.4":"cittam nibbattate mama. ","tha-ap57:6.1":"Labham tesam suladdhamva, ","tha-ap57:6.2":"ye labhantupasampadam; ","tha-ap57:6.3":"Punapi payirupaseyyam, ","tha-ap57:6.4":"buddho loke sace bhave. ","tha-ap57:7.1":"Atthavisatikkhattumham, ","tha-ap57:7.2":"raja asim mahabbalo; ","tha-ap57:7.3":"Caturanto vijitavi, ","tha-ap57:7.4":"jambusandassa issaro. ","tha-ap57:8.1":"Idam pacchimakam mayham, ","tha-ap57:8.2":"carimo vattate bhavo; ","tha-ap57:8.3":"Pattosmi acalam thanam, ","tha-ap57:8.4":"hitva jayaparajayam. ","tha-ap57:9.1":"Catutimsasahassamhi, ","tha-ap57:9.2":"mahatejosi khattiyo; ","tha-ap57:9.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap57:9.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap57:10.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap57:10.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap57:10.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap57:11.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma opavayho thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap57:12.1":"Opavayhattherassapadanam pancamam. "}